    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ 425°F/ Gas 7</p><p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Slice the<strong> whole butternut squash</strong> in half, then scoop out and discard the seeds</p><p>Tip: For easier cutting, use a bread knife (oiling the knife helps too!)</p>",
